<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HR One - Connexion</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logo-rh.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/auth-pro.css?v=3">
    <style>
        .logo-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }
        .logo-large {
            width: 90px;
            height: 90px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 12px 32px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2));
            margin: 0 auto 16px;
            display: block;
        }
        .logo-subtitle-large {
            margin: 8px 0 0;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }
        .logo-text {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
        }
        .dashboard-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 12px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 13px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .dashboard-link:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        .footer-content {
            max-width: 1120px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .footer-logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #2563eb;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .footer-logo-svg {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .footer-logo-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .footer-logo-subtitle {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #64748b;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .footer-copyright {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: #64748b;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        body.auth-standalone {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .auth-page {
            flex: 1;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .footer-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
                gap: 20px;
            }

            .footer-links {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="auth-standalone">
<main class="auth-page">
    <section class="auth-container auth-login-layout">
        <aside class="auth-panel auth-brand">
            <div class="logo-section">
                <svg class="logo-large" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <rect x="4" y="4" width="32" height="32" rx="6" fill="white" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                    <rect x="10" y="10" width="6" height="6" fill="#2563eb" rx="1"/>
                    <rect x="24" y="10" width="6" height="6" fill="#2563eb" rx="1"/>
                    <line x1="10" y1="20" x2="30" y2="20" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                    <rect x="10" y="26" width="6" height="6" fill="#2563eb" rx="1"/>
                    <rect x="24" y="26" width="6" height="6" fill="#2563eb" rx="1"/>
                </svg>
                <h1>HR One</h1>
                <p class="logo-subtitle-large">Espace RH</p>
            </div>
            <p class="auth-brand-copy">
                Connectez-vous à votre espace pour gérer les formations, la communauté et les flux RH dans une interface unique.
            </p>
            <ul class="auth-feature-list">
                <li><strong>RH:</strong> Ouverture sur le sidebar RH (gestion, offres, entretiens, formations, evenements, conges, communaute)</li>
                <li><strong>Candidat:</strong> Accès ciblé aux offres d'emploi et aux candidatures</li>
                <li><strong>Employé:</strong> Accès aux modules communaute, formations, participations, evenements et conges</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="auth-brand-links">
                <a href="{{ path('app_register_rh') }}" class="brand-link">Créer compte RH</a>
                <a href="{{ path('app_register_employee') }}" class="brand-link">Créer compte Employé</a>
                <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}" class="brand-link">Créer compte Candidat</a>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <section class="auth-panel">
            <header class="auth-panel-header">
                <p class="auth-eyebrow">🔐 Authentification</p>
                <h2>Connexion</h2>
                <p class="auth-subtitle">Entrez votre email (ou nom utilisateur) et votre mot de passe pour accéder à votre espace personnel.</p>
            </header>

            <div class="auth-flash-list">
                {% if error %}
                    <div class="auth-flash error">
                        <strong>Erreur:</strong> {{ error.messageKey|trans(error.messageData, 'security') }}
                    </div>
                {% endif %}
                {% for message in app.flashes('success') %}
                    <div class="auth-flash success">
                        <strong>Succès:</strong> {{ message }}
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>

            <form method="post" class="auth-form" novalidate>
                <div class="auth-field">
                    <label for="email">📧 Email ou Nom d'utilisateur</label>
                    <input 
                        id="email" 
                        name="email" 
                        value="{{ last_username }}" 
                        autocomplete="username" 
                        placeholder="nom@email.com ou utilisateur"
                        required 
                        autofocus
                        class="auth-input">
                </div>

                <div class="auth-field">
                    <label for="password">🔑 Mot de passe</label>
                    <input 
                        id="password" 
                        type="password" 
                        name="password" 
                        autocomplete="current-password"
                        placeholder="••••••••"
                        required
                        class="auth-input">
                </div>

                <div class="auth-field">
                    <label for="captcha_answer">✓ Captcha</label>
                    <div class="auth-captcha-box">
                        <span class="auth-captcha-question">Résoudre: <strong>{{ captcha_question }}</strong></span>
                        <input 
                            id="captcha_answer" 
                            name="captcha_answer" 
                            inputmode="numeric" 
                            pattern="[0-9]*" 
                            placeholder="Votre réponse"
                            required
                            class="auth-input">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <input type="hidden" name="_csrf_token" value="{{ csrf_token('authenticate') }}">

                <div class="auth-action-row">
                    <button class="auth-btn-primary" type="submit">
                        <span>Se connecter</span>
                        <span class="btn-icon">→</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>

            <div class="auth-separator">
                <span>Ou</span>
            </div>

            <div class="auth-link-list">
                <div class="link-group">
                    <p class="link-label">Pas encore inscrit?</p>
                    <a href="{{ path('app_register_rh') }}" class="auth-link">Inscription RH</a>
                    <a href="{{ path('app_register_employee') }}" class="auth-link">Inscription Employé</a>
                    <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}" class="auth-link">Inscription Candidat</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </section>
</main>

<footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-content">
        <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}" class="footer-logo">
            <svg class="footer-logo-svg" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <rect x="4" y="4" width="32" height="32" rx="6" fill="white" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2"/>
                <rect x="10" y="10" width="6" height="6" fill="#2563eb" rx="1"/>
                <rect x="24" y="10" width="6" height="6" fill="#2563eb" rx="1"/>
                <line x1="10" y1="20" x2="30" y2="20" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <rect x="10" y="26" width="6" height="6" fill="#2563eb" rx="1"/>
                <rect x="24" y="26" width="6" height="6" fill="#2563eb" rx="1"/>
            </svg>
            <div>
                <div class="footer-logo-title">HR One</div>
                <div class="footer-logo-subtitle">Espace RH</div>
            </div>
        </a>
        <p class="footer-copyright">&copy; 2024-2026 HR One - Plateforme RH Intégrée</p>
        <ul class="footer-links">
            <li><a href="#privacy">Politique de confidentialité</a></li>
            <li><a href="#terms">Conditions d'utilisation</a></li>
            <li><a href="#help">Aide</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
